<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Erreur serveur - Energreen</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@700&family=Montserrat:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
<style>
    body {
        background-color: #f0f4f1;
        font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
        color: #1a361c;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 50px;
    }
    .error-container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 50px auto;
        background: white;
        padding: 40px;
        border-radius: 15px;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        border-top: 5px solid #dc3545; /* Couleur rouge pour 500 */
    }
    h1 {
        font-size: 4rem;
        color: #dc3545;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    h2 {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
        color: #1a361c;
        margin-bottom: 25px;
    }
    p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: #555;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .btn-action {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 25px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: bold;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        margin: 0 10px;
    }
    .btn-retry {
        background-color: #0d6efd; /* Bleu Bootstrap */
        color: white;
    }
    .btn-retry:hover {
        background-color: #0b5ed7;
        transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    .btn-dashboard {
        background-color: #1a361c;
        color: white;
    }
    .btn-dashboard:hover {
        background-color: #142a15;
        transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
</style>
<div class="error-container">
    <h1>500</h1>
    <h2>Erreur interne du serveur</h2>
    <p>Une erreur inattendue est survenue. Veuillez réessayer plus tard.</p>
    <a href="javascript:location.reload()" class="btn-action btn-retry">Réessayer</a>
    <a href="/dashboard" class="btn-action btn-dashboard">Retour au tableau de bord</a>
</div>
</body>
</html>
